p: The MS analysis was performed on a maXis HD Q-TOF/MS (Bruker, Germany) using an ESI source. The capillary voltage was 3200 V and 3500 V in negative and positive mode, respectively. The scanning mass range ( m/z) was 50–1500 and spectra rate was 1.00 Hz. The nebulizer pressure, dry gas temperature and continuous dry gas flow rate were set at 2.0 Bar, 230 °C, and 8 L/min, respectively.
